54.6	Bloody_Mary_(cocktail)	Bloody Mary (cocktail)	A Bloody Mary is a popular cocktail containing vodka, tomato juice, and usually other spices or flavorings such as Worcestershire sauce, Tabasco sauce, piri piri sauce, beef consomme or bouillon, horseradish, celery, olive, salt, black pepper, cayenne pepper, lemon juice, and celery salt. It has been called "the world's most complex cocktail."	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/12/Bloody_Mary.jpg/220px-Bloody_Mary.jpg
